I"Ë<p>My PhD funding came from teaching assistantships, which meant that I was
a TA every quarter in grad school. Consequently, I have a variety of
courses under my belt.</p>

<p>In rough order of relevance.</p>

<h2 id="game-design-studio">Game Design Studio</h2>

<p><small class="gray">
alongside Rob Zubek
</small> <big>|</big> <small class="gray">Winter
2017, 2018, 2019, 2020
</small></p>

<p>Students create a shippable game from scratch in Unity3D and C# in a studio-style environment with instructor critique and guidance.</p>

