<h2 id="game-design-and-development">Game Design and Development</h2>

<p><small class="gray">
alongside Ian Horswill
</small> <big>|</big> <small class="gray">Fall
2016, 2017
</small></p>

<p>Students learn the ropes of Unity3D and C# gameplay programming. Topics include, among other things, rendering, physics, input, pathfinding, and serialization.</p>

