<h2 id="game-design-studio-ii">Game Design Studio II</h2>

<p><small class="gray">
taught by me
</small> <big>|</big> <small class="gray">Spring
2018
</small></p>

<p>Games industry-bound students create a game from scratch in teams of three using Unity3 and C#. Advanced iteration of the original game design studio.</p>

<h2 id="data-structures">Data Structures</h2>

<p><small class="gray">
alongside Vincent St. Amour
</small> <big>|</big> <small class="gray">Spring
2020
</small></p>

<p>Students learn the fundamentals of algorithms, runtime complexity, and data structures in a python-adjacent language. Heavy on system design and unit testing.</p>

