<h2 id="data-structures-1">Data Structures</h2>

<p><small class="gray">
alongside Ian Horswill
</small> <big>|</big> <small class="gray">Spring
2018
</small></p>

<p>Students learn the fundamentals of algorithms, runtime complexity, and data structures in C#. Heavy on theoretical reasoning and proofs.</p>

